scene.message:
Nanjo: That old man... is he{nl}
serious, or just having us{nl}
on...{waitkey}{ret}

Old Man: Listen, Hiroshi. The{nl}
human heart is a complex{nl}
thing.{waitkey}{clearbox}What shows on the surface{nl}
isn't always a person's{nl}
true heart.{waitkey}{clearbox}You must seek out the truth{nl}
hidden beneath...{waitkey}{ret}

Nurse: Hiroshi is apparently{nl}
his grandson's name.{waitkey}And me, I'm being mistaken{nl}
for his daughter...{waitkey}{ret}
